node.text:
🏆 To all the people who follow me, volleyball players, coaches, fans, Americans and non-Americans. Here is the message:

🗣 Don’t worry about what anyone else thinks of what you choose for you. You can choose success. It doesn’t have to be stumbled into. Decide success is happiness.

node.text:
James Kent demonstrating the long-way back set. Being able to go against the flow of the play is crucial once you’re at a high level.

James is coming off winning the 18 open gold medal 🥇 with his club team and is pursuing college volleyball heading into his 12th grade year and second year of 18s.

Comment what area you’re from. We like to know.

#SetterCollege #Volleyball #NotJustForSetters @hittercollegevb @liberocollegevb

This is my girl… KP

Her work is an example of how I would push all of you who direct message us each day to work.

Commitment to the system and HER work have literally shifted her volleyball trajectory and life trajectory. Gaining confidence. Gaining skill. Gaining IQ and believing in her internal beauty.

Note youth: one’s team or two’s team matters less. Position matters less. Experience matters less. What matters most is what you do with your opportunity. Once KP connect with @settercollegevb & @volleyballlessons , all 🔥.

#SetterCollege #Volleyball #NotJustForSetters @kaylao.vb
